Lighter Box will, hopefully, be a simple HTML overlay pop-up in the spirit
of lightbox that can be applied to any block content. The name might be
changed at some point in the future.

CURRENTLY IN ALPHA - USE ONLY FOR TESTING.
NO WARRANTY FOR THIS FREE SOFTWARE! USE IT AT YOUR OWN RISK!

	
